text:
The reserved words ( jsp, _jsp, jspx, _jspx, java, servlet, sun, sunw ) are
accepted as value for the prefix attribute of the taglib directive.

creator: kin-man.chung@sun.com
text:
Mmm... The spec (Table JSP.2-1) only list the following reserved prefixes:

jsp, jspx, java, javax, servlet, sun, and sunw
